      <title>《鱿鱼游戏 2》评价褒贬不一，但仍位居 Netflix 全球排行榜榜首</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-02/-squid-game-season-2-tops-charts-despite-mixed-reviews-video</link>
